= Qubes-Whonix =
Instead of applying [https://www.qubes-os.org/doc/language-localization/ language localization input] on a per VM basis, the following [https://github.com/QubesOS/qubes-doc/pull/340/commits/eea10c71415f93bbf9e2eae5a9ef50ffeaf06789 workaround] will correctly apply changes system-wide. <ref>Users report problems with the <code>System Tools</code> -> <code>Keyboard</code> -> <code>Layout</code> method in dom0, since [https://github.com/QubesOS/qubes-issues/issues/1396 the change does not propagate to other VMs].</ref>

If problems are encountered, see: [https://www.qubes-os.org/faq/#my-keyboard-layout-settings-are-not-behaving-correctly-what-should-i-do My keyboard layout settings are not behaving correctly. What should I do?] in the Qubes FAQ.

